    "excerpt": "<p>There was already a Request and changed.</p>\n<aside class=\"quote quote-modified\" data-post=\"27\" data-topic=\"2699\">\n  <div class=\"title\">\n    <div class=\"quote-controls\"></div>\n    <img alt=\"\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" src=\"https://community.signalusers.org/user_avatar/community.signalusers.org/racer_77/48/52690_2.png\" class=\"avatar\">\n    <div class=\"quote-title__text-content\">\n      <a href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/t/save-pictures-to-pictures-signal-instead-of-pictures-or-configure-where-media-attachments-are-saved/2699/27\">Save pictures to /Pictures/Signal/ instead of /Pictures/ or Configure where media attachments are saved</a> <a class=\"badge-category__wrapper \" href=\"/c/feature-requests/android-feature-requests/18\"><span data-category-id=\"18\" style=\"--category-badge-color: #2D8B39; --category-badge-text-color: #FFFFFF; --parent-category-badge-color: #83B72A;\" data-parent-category-id=\"17\" data-drop-close=\"true\" class=\"badge-category --style-square --has-parent\"><span class=\"badge-category__name\">Android Feature Requests</span></span></a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <blockquote>\n    This was accepted and merged in 7.52<a href=\"#footnote-275666-1\" id=\"footnote-ref-275666-1\">[1]</a>: \n\n\nImages: Pictures/Signal/\nVideos: Movies/Signal/\nAudio: Music/Signal/<a href=\"#footnote-275666-2\" id=\"footnote-ref-275666-2\">[2]</a>\n\n\nAnd for saved documents: \n\nThe approach now maintains the existing behavior: \n\nAndroid 9-: Documents/Signal/ (as it was Documents/ before)\nAndroid 10+: Download/Signal/ (as it was Download/ before)<a href=\"#footnote-275666-3\" id=\"footnote-ref-275666-3\">[3]</a>\n\n\n\n\n\n <a href=\"https://github.com/signalapp/Signal-Android/commit/50d809029ef159e5b030d40d880e8ba3a11f4d9c\" class=\"inline-onebox\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Save media attachments to Signal subdirectories. · signalapp/Signal-Android@50d8090 · GitHub</a> <a href=\"#footnote-ref-275666-1\" class=\"footnote-backref\"><img width=\"20\" height=\"20\" src=\"https://community.signalusers.org/images/emoji/apple/right_arrow_curving_left.png?v=15\" title=\"right_arrow_curving_left\" alt=\"right_arrow_curving_left\" class=\"emoji\">︎</a> \n\n <a href=\"https://github.com/signalapp/Signal-Android/pull/14277#issuecomment-3152163350\" class=\"inline-onebox\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Save image attachments to Pictures/Signal subdirectory by Verryx-02 · Pull R…</a>\n  </blockquote>\n</aside>\n"
